# Always re-check HTML so a browser never runs a stale page that points at JS
# chunks deleted by a newer deploy (the cause of intermittent "client-side
# exception" errors that a refresh fixes). Hashed build assets are safe to
# cache forever. Placed in public/ so it ships inside the deployed out/ folder.

/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=0, must-revalidate

/_next/static/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=31536000, immutable
